<D>__{you're all right, charlie. i'm glad you stopped by. i'm sorry if well i know i sometimes run on.}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{hell no! jesus, i'm the kind of guy, i will let you know if i'm bored. i find it all pretty damned interesting. i'm the kind schmoe who's generally interested in the other guy's point of view.}
