<B>__{his pov}
<A>__{the bathing beauty. from offscreen we hear a sticky, adhesive giving way sound.}
<C>__{barton}
<D>__{he looks around to the opposite bed wall.}
<B>__{his pov}
<A>__{the wallpaper is lightly sheened with moisture from the heat. one swath of wallpaper is just finishing sagging away from the wall. about three feet of the wall, where it meets the ceiling, is exposed. the strip of wallpaper, its glue apparently melted, sags and nods above the bed. it glistens yellow, like a fleshy tropical flower.}
<B>__{back to barton}
<A>__{he goes over to the bed and steps up onto it. he smooths the wallpaper back up against the wall. he looks at his hand.}
<B>__{his hand}
<A>__{sticky with tacky yellow wall sweat. he wipes it onto his shirt. we hear a faint mosquito hum. barton looks around.}
